title: (1) My Mix IEX–16L 16 Channel Input Expander
item_description:
(1) My Mix IEX–16L 16 Channel Input Expander

(1) My Mix IEX–16L (16) Channel Input Expander

  • includes 19 inch rack mount (16) channel unit
  • Power supply included
  • network PSU included
  • (16) channel breakout snake included
  • additional breakout snake included
  • (16) channel input expander for line level signals. Expands a myMix system by 16 audio channels.*
  • Includes power supply
  • DB25 connectors for line level signals (“Tascam” pin out)
  • Save input configuration with channel mode, names and input gain settings
  • Can be locked through CONFIG port
  • Large dual color LEDS for signal present and clip
